er Middle Ages <i>Hugh</i> has also been used as an Anglicized form of the Gaelic name Aodh ."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Bright’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Hugh de Bolebec was born about 1050, in Normandy, France as the son of Hugues de Bolbec and Unknown. He married Unknown before 1075, in France. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died about 1100, at the age of 52."},"et":{"about 1050–about 1100":"umbes 1050–umbes 1100","1050–1100":"1050–1100","–Female":"Surnud","1075–1164":"1075–1164","1036–Male":"1036–Surnud","about 1050":"umbes 1050","1036":"1036","1100":"1100","before 1075":"enne 1075","1164":"1164","Aft 1075":"pärast 1075","1075":"1075","about 1100":"umbes 1100","before 1050":"enne 1050","1050":"1050","Normandie, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa","France":"Prantsusmaa","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1050–about 1100":"noin 1050–noin 1100","1050–1100":"1050–1100","–Female":"Kuollut","1075–1164":"1075–1164","1036–Male":"1036–Kuollut","about 1050":"noin 1050","1036":"1036","1100":"1100","before 1075":"ennen vuotta 1075","1164":"1164","Aft 1075":"1075 jälkeen","1075":"1075","about 1100":"noin 1100","before 1050":"ennen vuotta 1050","1050":"1050","Normandie, France":"Normandie, Ranska","France":"Ranska","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1050–about 1100":"environ 1050–environ 1100","1050–1100":"1050–1100","–Female":"Décédée","1075–1164":"1075–1164","1036–Male":"1036–Décédé","about 1050":"environ 1050","1036":"1036","1100":"1100","before 1075":"avant 1075","1164":"1164","Aft 1075":"après 1075","1075":"1075","about 1100":"environ 1100","before 1050":"avant 1050","1050":"1050","Normandie, France":"Normandie, France","France":"France","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France","lifeSummary":"Hugh de Bolebec est né environ 1050, à Normandie, France, fils de Hugues de Bolbec et Unknown. Il a 